articles.title: U.S. and allies suspend training of Iraqi forces: Germany
articles.description: The United States and its allies have suspended training of Iraqi forces due to the increased threat they face after a U.S. air strike in Baghdad on Friday killed a top Iranian general, the German military said in a letter seen by Reuters.
